{"tid":1480621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【心事台】有無人入嚟開導下我","createTime":"2019-08-17T11:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T23:15:02.000Z","uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a03023db784ef1f5c3a6a82f42d07497f2244d8a","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:27:48.000Z","msg":"家陣好心寒 好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說我而家係外國讀緊書 身邊有幾個特別close既大陸同學<br />\n<br />\n雖然我地無特別避傾時事 但係我知普遍大陸人都係愛國 所以都無特別提。<br />\n<br />\n後尾七月中有略略傾過一兩句 但係見佢地無咩反應 所以以為佢地出得嚟接觸多啲外國新聞就發現中國既封閉程度，亦都可能會係外國人談論中國既態度入面明白到中國潛在既問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知相反。<br />\n俾咁大個機會佢地接觸外面世界<br />\n仲有多元化地唔同角度地分析同一單新聞既news source<br />\n佢地就鐘情於火牆入面既qq微博<br />\n仲要淨係識睇單一化而且bias到pk既資訊源<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最仆街既係有個係外國土生土長既女仔，明明連大陸都未住過 竟然唔知癡咗邊條線 愛國奶共程度超過哂一般中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後家陣啲共匪開行turbo搞 我支持警察單野，佢地果然就即刻仆哂出嚟支持，我真係屌哂佢地老母。一開佢地ig story全部都係please respect the history hong kong is part of china<br />\n<br />\n完全睇錯佢地。<br />\n好失望。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知好多巴絲都有類似經驗 有無人可以分享下你地點做？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總知可唔可以幫我分散下注意力 唔想不斷諗住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9830cfb76c72475e816004d4779983e5b2377649","tid":1480621,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:29:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一日有聯繫匯率<br />\n一日keep美金相等於keep港紙<br />\n換美金再換返港元會蝕少少匯差<br />\n但當聯繫匯率維持唔到<br />\n你估係港元唔得定美金唔得呀嗱？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"ddeaf60cdb85095a3caa277339632346a11394e3","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"利申<br />\n佢地其實人品唔錯<br />\n亦對朋友好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857e5de18831874a25dfb0404ea3855416aa0a29","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"你地係點面對身邊既藍絲朋友家人親戚？"},{"pid":"e7fed1de0fd133c4e0f4cea1366dc9485284de00","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:31:41.000Z","msg":"算<br />\n打下自己感受都好"},{"pid":"031cf416a2ad09f078c2dcd5781f6b4fd72bab25","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:32:22.000Z","msg":"越諗越火滾"},{"pid":"07d2ed5e88661ac3a7911506599a1f174ed0e8f7","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031cf416a2ad09f078c2dcd5781f6b4fd72bab25","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:32:22.000Z","msg":"越諗越火滾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"dnlm共產黨<br />\n分化人民<br />\n黑講成白<br />\n白講成黑"},{"pid":"1b3f265482c37170393d84bca9e01e263f20a6d3","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"身邊唯一一個香港人又鬼咁死奶共<br />\n之後淨番嗰啲就全部外國人"},{"pid":"135211b06c9a8e2abe0e01279b7c17d166f4c6d3","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:37:27.000Z","msg":"有少少柒<br />\n得我自言自語"},{"pid":"a136a5bf70e9c03de70343e68ce167bcd1ef1b78","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"135211b06c9a8e2abe0e01279b7c17d166f4c6d3","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:37:27.000Z","msg":"有少少柒<br />\n得我自言自語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"是但<br />\n火都嚟埋<br />\n<br />\n見到佢地話支持警察真係想一巴星埋去"},{"pid":"8bf445c839223916dc7ef08f023a3255cb59dcba","tid":1480621,"uid":293729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":